\\e[1;34m🛠️ Welcome to Alpine Toolbox!\\e[0m
You have curl, dig, traceroute, nc, tcpdump, ip, etc.

Example commands:
curl -vk --connect-timeout 10 https://\\$KUBERNETES_SERVICE_HOST:443/version
curl -vk --cacert /var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/ca.crt -H \\"Authorization: Bearer \$(cat /var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token)\\" --connect-timeout 10 https://\\$KUBERNETES_SERVICE_HOST:443/api/v1/nodes

curl -vk http://servicename.namespace.svc:port/path/to/metrics